title: DDFP 278: Daniel Jeremiah & Michael Fabiano
itunes:title: DDFP 278: Daniel Jeremiah & Michael Fabiano
description:
Shek is joined by old pal and former NFL scout Daniel Jeremiah to discuss the early developments from training camps including the Sammy Watkins' hype, Chip Kelly's offense in year two and the New York Giants. "NFL Fantasy Live" analyst Michael Fabiano then previews the fantasy value of Johnny Manziel and other young quarterbacks like RGIII and Colin Kaepernick.
